    "monster4708": "<h1 class=monster>Great Ape<br><span class=type>Medium natural beast</span><br><span class=level>Level 4 Skirmisher<span class=xp> XP 175</span></span></h1><table class=bodytable><tr><td><b>HP</b> 55; <b>Bloodied</b> 27<td class=rightalign><b>Initiative</b> +6<tr><td><b>AC</b> 18, <b>Fortitude</b> 18, <b>Reflex</b> 16, <b>Will</b> 16<td class=rightalign><b>Perception</b>+4<tr><td><b>Speed</b> 7, climb 6<td class=rightalign>Low-light vision<tr><td colspan=2></table><h2>Traits</h2><p class=flavorIndent> <b>Swift Climber</b> </p><p class=flavorIndent>The ape does not provoke opportunity attacks by climbing.</p><h2>Standard Actions</h2><p class=flavorIndent>(⚔) <b>Slam</b> ✦ <b>At-Will</b></p><p class=flavorIndent><i>Attack:</i> Melee 1 (one creature); +9 vs. AC</p><p class=flavorIndent><i>Hit:</i> 2d6+5 damage.</p><p class='flavor alt'>⚔ <b>On the Run</b> ✦ <b>At-Will</b></p><p class=flavorIndent><i>Effect:</i> The ape shifts or climbs half its speed and uses slam at any point during the move.</p><p class='flavor alt'>⚔ <b>Felling Blow</b> ✦ Recharge ⚅</p><p class=flavorIndent><i>Effect:</i> The ape uses slam twice against the same target. If both attacks hit, the target falls prone.</p><p class='flavor alt'><b>Skills</b> Athletics +11<br> <b>Str</b> 19 (+6)                <b>Dex</b> 15 (+4)                <b>Wis</b> 14 (+4)<br><b>Con</b> 15 (+4)                <b>Int</b> 2 (-2)                <b>Cha</b> 8 (+1)</p><p class=flavor><b>Alignment</b> Unaligned       <b> Languages</b> -</p><p class=publishedIn>Published in Monster Manual 3, page(s) 10, Dungeon Magazine 192.</p>",
